OL,5, Pupils could miss out on school trips  
OL,6, and music lessons as schools face      
OL,7, rising costs this year, head teachers  
OL,8, have told BBC News.                    
OL,10,FSome school leaders in England say     
OL,11,Fthese are among the areas they would   
OL,12,Ftrim first, before reducing staff.     
OL,14,FThey are grappling with staffing costs 
OL,15,Fand are being hit particularly hard by 
OL,16,Frising energy bills.                   
OL,18,FThe government says it is increasing   
OL,19,Fbudgets for schools and helping them by
OL,20,Frecommending energy deals.             
